Gasoline Alley | Full Hollywood Action Thriller Movie | Bruce Willis | Luke Wilson | Devon Sawa

Jimmy Jayne (Devon Sawa), a bruised-fisted rockabilly boss-type is sucked into the savage murder of four Hollywood starlets found dead in a sordid motel after he was last seen entertaining one of the women at the hotel bar. Becoming the prime suspect for Homicide Detectives Freeman (Bruce Willis) and Vargas (Luke Wilson), Jimmy takes up his own rogue investigation to clear his name, bending the law in ways the police canâ€™t. With several suspects skating through his shadow, he relentlessly searches for the killer at high dollar parties, porn-star mansions, drug dens and auto shops, driving a hailstorm of martial arts combat and high-speed car chases.

2022.  Stars: Bruce Willis, Luke Wilson, Devon Sawa
